<h1><a name=groups></a>Managing Groups</h1>

<p>You add, edit, and delete groups on this page. Groups define templates 
 for the privileges that apply to individual user inboxes. All of the inboxes 
 assigned to a group have the same voicemail privileges, such as inbox 
 size and length of outgoing message. </p>

<p>It is the group to which an individual inbox belongs that determines 
 the privilege settings that apply. You establish inbox privileges by associating 
 each inbox with a group when you first add the voice mailbox.</p>

<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Remember:</span> Adding and deleting 
 groups does not add and delete users. It adds and deletes privilege templates.</p>

